**/.idea
**/.DS_Store

# Ephemeral skill run artifacts (component network HTML/JS, MCP dumps, etc.)
.cursor/skills/cja-component-visualizer/outputs/

# Dimension survey: chat/run-only payloads and MCP scratch (keep scripts/ for committed configs)
